## ğŸ¨ Color Scheme

- **Primary Blue**: `#0066cc` - Main accent color
- **Dark Text**: `#000000` - Body text
- **White**: `#ffffff` - Backgrounds & text
- **Light Blue**: `#e6f0ff` - About section background
- **Dark Background**: `#1a1a1a` - Footer background

## ğŸ“± Responsive Breakpoints

- **Desktop**: Full width layouts
- **Tablet**: (768px and below) - Adjusted spacing and layouts
- **Mobile**: Stacked components, single column layouts

## ğŸ”§ How to Customize

### Modifying the Header
Edit `components/header.js` - `renderHeader()` function:
```javascript
// Change logo text
<div class="logo">Your Brand Name</div>

// Add/remove navigation items
<a href="#section">Menu Item</a>
```

### Changing Colors
Edit the CSS variables in `styles.css`:
```css
:root {
    --primary-blue: #0066cc;      /* Change primary color */
    --dark-text: #000;             /* Change text color */
    /* ... other colors */
}
```

### Adding Destination Cards
Edit `components/destinations.js` - Add to the `destinations` array:
```javascript
{
    name: 'Your Destination',
    description: 'Description here',
    attractions: ['Attraction 1', 'Attraction 2'],
    popular: true  // Set to true to show Popular badge
}
```

### Modifying Features
Edit `components/features.js` - Update the `features` array:
```javascript
{
    title: 'Feature Name',
    description: 'Your description',
    icon: 'ğŸ¯',  // Change emoji icon
    highlights: ['Item 1', 'Item 2'],
    imagePosition: 'right'  // or 'left'
}
```

### Editing About Section Features
Edit `components/about.js` - Modify the `aboutFeatures` array:
```javascript
{
    icon: 'ğŸŒ',
    title: 'Feature Title',
    description: 'Feature description text'
}
```

## ğŸ¯ Key Features

### 1. **Modular Architecture**
- Each section is in its own JavaScript file
- Easy to maintain, update, and debug
- Clean separation of concerns

### 2. **Responsive Design**
- Mobile-first approach
- Flexbox and CSS Grid layouts
- Touch-friendly buttons and spacing

### 3. **Smooth Animations**
- Scroll animations on load
- Hover effects on buttons and cards
- Smooth scrolling for navigation

### 4. **Event Handling**
- Download button handlers
- Watch demo functionality
- Plan trip actions
- Share with friends capability

### 5. **Accessibility**
- Semantic HTML structure
- Proper heading hierarchy
- Good color contrast
- Keyboard navigation support

## ğŸš€ Getting Started

1. **Download all files** and keep the folder structure intact
2. **Open `index.html`** in a web browser
3. **All sections load automatically** when the page loads
4. **No build process needed** - pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript

## ğŸ“ Customization Tips

### To change button text and colors:
1. Go to `styles.css` and find `.btn-primary` or `.btn-secondary`
2. Modify the background-color, text properties
3. Update the component JS files for button labels

### To add new sections:
1. Create a new div with an ID in `index.html`
2. Create a new JS file in `components/` folder
3. Add a render function similar to existing components
4. Link the script in `index.html`
5. Call the render function in `app.js`

### To add images:
Replace the placeholder colored divs with:
```html
<img src="path/to/image.jpg" alt="Description" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
```

