### CTA Section
- Conversion-focused section
- Multiple call-to-action buttons
- Statistics and social proof
- Blue gradient background

### Footer
- Company description
- Quick links
- Resource links
- Copyright information

## ğŸ› Troubleshooting

### Sections not showing?
- Make sure all script files are in the correct `components/` folder path
- Check browser console for JavaScript errors
- Verify file names match exactly in script tags

### Styling not applied?
- Clear browser cache (Ctrl+Shift+Delete)
- Check CSS file path is correct
- Verify no CSS conflicts

### Buttons not working?
- Check `app.js` event listeners are initialized
- Verify button class names match CSS
- Open browser console to see any errors

